text: What will be the output for the below query? SELECT Name FROM Employee WHERE Name IS 'S_ _ _ _ _ %'; (@) It will return names where number of characters in names are greater than or equals to 6 (b) It will return names where number of characters in names are greater than 6 (o) It will return names where number of characters in names are less than or equals to 6 (d) It will give an error
